{"type": "article", "id": 25371, "title": "互动式家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-13T07:14:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 56, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702172426rhP0dEI6nKt3o5OC.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这两件家具都能随着开合与人互动。抽屉的表面覆盖了一些小的“鳞片”，拉开抽屉的过程也拨动了“鳞片”本身，可以看到它像波浪一样滑动的效果。另一个柜子的柜门则会随着人的走动变换颜色，两种设计都带给空间更多的趣味。设计师 Juno Jeon 是在荷兰学习的韩国人，<a href=\"http://www.junojunos.com/\">这里是他的主页。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"medium-insert-active com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021724231JhEe8nzXvLqZgQ9.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172424VT6S7BpWlsxeU8bD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172424CH3SOMJmcvpqPRrs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.299511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172425p4RqxOIiTrDAjg5K.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172426Y9tpzy8Bk6KqhsPW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70660147\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}